---
title: Flujo de Estados CO (Solicitud de Credito)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending: create() / estado inicial

    pending --> fetching_bank_data: update_status() -- CO bootstrap → fetching_bank_data_task
    fetching_bank_data --> validate_country_rules: BankProviderData persistida -- validate_country_rules_task
    validate_country_rules --> approved: valid=true -- CountryValidation persistida
    validate_country_rules --> rejected: valid=false

    pending --> technical_error: bootstrap error
    fetching_bank_data --> technical_error: retries agotados / fallo proveedor
    validate_country_rules --> technical_error: retries agotados / datos faltantes

    approved --> [*]
    rejected --> [*]
    technical_error --> [*]

    note right of pending
        CO salta validación async de documento.
        Bootstrap inicia directamente en fetching_bank_data.
    end note

    note right of approved
        Estado terminal. on_enter dispara notify_final_decision_task.
        Webhook saliente si WEBHOOK_URL está configurada.
    end note
